'''Sal'kaasa''' was a small settlement on [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]].

Being on the fringes of the [[Bright Lands]], it was far from Ryloth's main urban zones like [[Kala'uun/Legends|Kala'uun]]. It had a spaceport and housed a small contingent of [[Rodian/Legends|Rodians]].

[[Dindoo]]'s mechanic shop and the business [[Dindoo Tours]], managed by Dindoo's heir [[Kelko]], were located on Sal'kaasa.

